# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

node_modules
# Published library build output. (The web demo's Vite build output lives in
# examples/web/dist, ignored by examples/web/.gitignore.)
dist_module
*.local

# This project uses Bun — ignore npm/yarn/pnpm lockfiles to avoid confusion.
# bun.lock (JSON format) is preferred and should be committed. These patterns are
# rootless, so they also cover the npm-based demos in examples/web and
# examples/native (which install with `npm` against a `file:` link) — their
# package-lock.json files are intentionally not committed.
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
pnpm-lock.yaml
bun.lockb

